Global Unmanaged Industrial Ethernet Switches Market Insights
Unmanaged Industrial Ethernet Switches Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Unmanaged Industrial Ethernet Switches Market Overview
The Unmanaged Industrial Ethernet Switches Market is poised for significant growth, with an estimated market size of USD 2.5 billion in 2024, and it is expected to grow at a CAGR of 8.4% from 2025 to 2030. The growth is attributed to the increasing adoption of industrial automation, smart manufacturing, and the expansion of industrial IoT (IIoT) networks. Unmanaged industrial Ethernet switches offer easy installation and a cost-effective solution for networking in harsh industrial environments, which makes them highly suitable for factories, warehouses, and outdoor installations. The market growth is driven by the demand for efficient and reliable connectivity solutions in diverse industrial applications like process control, factory automation, and transportation sectors.

